  "prompt": "How long HCL technology takes to give offer letter after document uploading round for experience?",
  "response": "The time it takes for HCL Technologies to issue an offer letter after the document uploading round can vary based on several factors, including the specific position, the volume of applicants, and internal processes. However, based on general feedback and experiences shared by candidates, you might expect the following timeline:\n\n1. **Document Verification**: This usually takes about 1-2 weeks after document submission.\n2. **Offer Letter Issuance**: After document verification, it may take an additional 1-2 weeks for the offer letter to be issued.\n\nSo, in total, you might expect to receive an offer letter within 2-4 weeks after uploading your documents. Keep in mind that this is a general estimate and actual times can vary.\n\nIf you haven't received any updates within this timeframe, it's advisable to follow up with the HR contact provided during your application process for more specific information.",
